               <msContents>
                  <summary>Gospel of John, ወንጌል፡ ዘዮሐንስ፡, ወንጌል፡ ዘዮሐንስ፡; Bandlet of Righteousness, Asmat Prayer, Prayer for the Journey to Heaven, Table Blessing, Absolution of the Son, ፍትሐት፡ ዘወልድ፡, Prayer “God of the Luminaries,” እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘብርሃናት፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="86v" facs="005"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT1693John"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>The text is arranged for the days of the week</note>
                  <explicit xml:lang="gez" type="supplication">
                    ኦ፡ አቡየ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ወመነኮስ።
                    ዘተሰመይከ፡ ገብረ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ቅዱስ።
                    ኢትርሥአኒ፡ ለፍቁርከ፡ ተክለ፡ ማርያም፡ ሐዲስ።
                    በይነ፡ ዘጸሐፍኩ፡ ለከ፡ ቃለ፡ ወንጌሉ፡ ለክርስቶስ።
                    ኁልቈ፡ ፩ዱ፡ አቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት፡ ለእንተ፡ ኢትመውት፡ ነፍስ።
                    ወበዝ፡ ዓለም፡ ለዕቅበተ፡ ሥጋየ፡ ንኡስ።
                  </explicit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="89r" to="102v" facs="093"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT1758Lefafa"/>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ አብ ወወልድ… መጽሐፈ ሕይወት ልፋፈ ጽድቅ ጸሎተ መድኃኒት ዘጸሐፈ አብ በእደዊሁ ቅዱሳት<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="117r" to="128v" facs="121"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> which Jesus gave to the disciples</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ አብ ወወልድ… ጸሎት ዘተስእልዎ አርዳኢሁ ለኢየሱስ ክርስቶስ ወይቤልዎ ክሥት ለነ እግዚኦ ዘንተ ስመከ ኅቡዓ<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="129r" to="135v" facs="133"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT1873Mangad"/>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ አብ ወወልድ… ጸሎተ መንገደ ሰማይ ዕቀበኒ ክርስቶስ ከመ ኢያዕቅፍዋ ለነፍስየ መላእክተ ጽልመት<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from="135v" to="145r" facs="140"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> spoken to Andrew</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ አብ ወወልድ… ጸሎት ዘተናገሮ ለእንድርያስ ሐዋርያ ጸሎቱ<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6"><locus from="145r" to="149v" facs="149"/><title>Table blessing, “We beseech you,” Sä’alnakä, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰአልናከ</foreign></title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ አብ ወወልድ… ሰአልናከ መሐሪ ሰአልናከ ፈጣሪ ሰአልናከ ከሃሊ ዘሰአሉከ ትሁብ<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7"><locus from="102r" to="109r" facs="106"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT1398Fethat"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ አብ ወወልድ… ጸሎተ ፍትሐት ዘወልድ እግዚእ እግዚኦ ኢየሱስ ክርስቶስ ወልድ ዋህድ ቃለ እግዚአብሔር አብ ዘበተከ እምኔነ<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8"><locus from="109v" to="113r" facs="114"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT3083RepCh363"/>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">እግዚአብሔር ዘብርሃናት እግዚአብሔር ዘሥልጣናት እግዚአብሔር ዘአርእስተ መላእክት<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
